          " مذهبه غلو."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.tashayyu": [
            "23 – ʿAbd al-Raḥmān b. Abū Ḥammād, Kufan.  Settled in Qum, and the Qummis narrated from him, he is known by the kunya “Abū Muḥammad”.  Very weak, he is not turned to, in his madhhab there is ghulw."
          ]
        }
      }
